item.title: starting a blog
item.description: I remember having a skyblog1 back in middle school, when basically everyone had one. But memories are blurry: I don’t even remeber what I was posting, probably some old school youtube links of songs I liked2 and pixelated images of some early-stage memes. Anyway, it hurts to say that more or less 15 years have passed since my last encounter with the world of blogs and shared some thoughts with the outside world.
